{"tid":1527184,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家請將個人身分證明文件放呢種袋","createTime":"2019-09-01T09:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T17:42:10.000Z","uid":9803,"like":624,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"29201939f075d1fa4b12deb67e3681cc481cc276","tid":1527184,"uid":9803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWUApU0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWUApU0.png&h=7b4c342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我上次去行山同行街成日週違走<br />\n我份人又大頭蝦成日懶低個袋走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又驚行街比人搶左個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢種袋最方便 最貼身<br />\n一黎無咁易好似背囊比賊仔一手搶走<br />\n二黎可以攞件衫遮住無咁易認到<br />\n三黎放身分證呢啲就夠晒用 其實水呀食物就放背囊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大家懶低左背囊或者比人搶走都唔洗保領身分證啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於行山我都唔主張帶信用卡嗰啲出街嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032bb33681f57e21461165e320e4fb9bd93c9164","tid":1527184,"uid":9803,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"係咪應該放時事台先多人理<br />\n但我個po係行山分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417bf2343a4bcbb8e3aa4204c53fa570b2189d0d","tid":1527184,"uid":9803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1071048cb877bacfcda118ca80fde91749a0b7","tid":1527184,"uid":271968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"推!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"fcc33cfc2f494b9f1359135fd3e27c9687fe8e81","tid":1527184,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse